   REEBOK INTERNATIONAL Ltd. (Stoughton, Mass.) -- David G.
Ropes was named to the newly created position of vice
president, marketing services, at the company's Reebok
division. Mr. Ropes will coordinate marketing support
services, including advertising, merchandising, celebrity
endorsements and retail promotions, the footwear and apparel
retailer said. Mr. Ropes previously was vice president of
advertising at Pepsi-Cola Co., a unit of PepsiCo Inc.,
Purchase, N.Y.
